      <section eId="sec_505">
        <num>505</num>
        <heading>Directors of facilities</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_505__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>operate and manage the facility,\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_505__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>submit a monthly report on such matters as the division may\nspecify.\n  3. Subject to the regulations of the division, the facility director\nmay authorize the use of the buildings and grounds of the facility by a\nmunicipality, special district or non-profit association, corporation or\norganization for educational, recreational, social and civic purposes\nwhenever such use may promote better relationships with the community in\nwhich the facility is located, provided, however, that such use does not\ninterfere with the purposes and program of the facility.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
